Today is the 3rd day of Amazon’s 12 days of deals and it’s focusing on home and kitchen products. I browsed through some of the offerings to pull out some items that I thought might be interesting to Gadgeteers and this is what I came up with for today: You’ll never have to push a vacuum again with the iRobot Roomba 614 Robotic Vacuum Cleaner which is 34% off today at $249.99. Make sure your holiday ham or turkey is fully cooked with a Harbor Stainless Steel digital cooking thermometer for $9.99. Your favorite shutter bug would love a Mango Spot Best Camera Lens Thermos Stainless Steel Cup/ Mug for $7.99 – $10.99. Keep warm with the Dr Infrared Heater Portable Space Heater for $84.99. I have one of these (different brand) and use it all the time in my chilly basement this time of year. 
Those are just 5 deals that caught my eye. You can shop all of today’s deals at Amazon’s 12 days of deals page. Share this story
